ZH: 灾害可能会给人类造成巨大的损失。
EN: Disasters may cause tremendous damage to humanity.

ZH: 北方地区经常遭受天灾人祸的灾害。
EN: The northern regions often suffer from natural and man-made disasters.

ZH: 珍惜水资源，减少因干旱引发的灾害。
EN: Conserve water resources to reduce disasters caused by drought.

ZH: 地震是一种常见的自然灾害。
EN: Earthquakes are a common natural disaster.

ZH: 必须制定应急预案以减少灾害的影响。
EN: Emergency plans must be developed to lessen the impact of disasters.

ZH: 希望所有受灾群众都能尽快恢复正常生活。
EN: Hope all affected residents can resume their normal lives soon.

ZH: 暴雨引发了洪水灾害。
EN: Heavy rain triggered a flood disaster.

ZH: 防止森林火灾是保护生态环境的重要举措。
EN: Preventing forest fires is an important measure to protect the environment.

ZH: 灾害教育应该成为学校课程的一部分。
EN: Disaster education should be part of school curriculum.

ZH: 社会各界必须积极参与防灾减灾工作。
EN: All sectors of society must actively participate in disaster prevention and reduction efforts.

ZH: 农作物受到了灾害的严重影响。
EN: Crops have been severely affected by the disaster.

ZH: 建筑物坍塌是地震灾害中的一个常见现象。
EN: Building collapse is a common phenomenon in earthquake disasters.

ZH: 灾害监测系统的建设对减少损失至关重要。
EN: The construction of disaster monitoring systems is crucial for reducing losses.

ZH: 食品安全问题也是一种潜在的灾害。
EN: Food safety issues are also a potential disaster.

ZH: 人们需要保持警惕，防止火灾等灾害的发生。
EN: People need to stay vigilant to prevent disasters such as fires.

ZH: 防灾减灾意识需要不断提高。
EN: Disaster prevention and reduction awareness needs to be constantly raised.

ZH: 牛年洪涝灾害导致大量农田被淹没。
EN: Flooding disasters in the Year of the Ox caused extensive farmland to be submerged.

ZH: 暴雪灾害使交通瘫痪了。
EN: Snowstorm disasters paralyzed transportation.

ZH: 立法现在已经禁止在易受灾害的地区盖房子。
EN: Legislation now prohibits building houses in disaster-prone areas. 

ZH: 确保所有居民都参与到防灾减灾工作中。
EN: Ensure that all residents are involved in disaster prevention and reduction work.
